    <Label name="lblExplanation" id="80606543-22ae-4bbd-a3fb-1be5bce259b5">
        <caption>For each icon:

The class of the picture is CM_NavigatorPicture

the HELPKEYWORD field has the value used in Root.getConfig() to access the picture ICON
the TAG field has the value used in Root.getConfig() to access the picture UP
the HYPERLINK field has the value used in Root.getConfig() to access the picture DOWN


the BUBBLEHELP field has the name of the picture file on the disk, minus .png
the DESCRIPTION field has the caption used in the navigator
the NAME field is generated from the HELPKEYWORD value where a space has been replaced for an under score character

The pictures will be loaded to Root.setConfig using all instances of CM_MenuEntityPicture</caption>
        <transparent/>
        <wordWrap/>
        <fontName>Verdana</fontName>
        <fontSize>12</fontSize>
        <foreColor>-2147483640</foreColor>
        <parent name="CM_MenuEntityIcons"/>
        <parentBottomOffset>284</parentBottomOffset>
        <parentRightOffset>22</parentRightOffset>
        <show3D>3</show3D>
        <tabIndex>9</tabIndex>
        <backColor>-2147483633</backColor>
        <enabled/>
        <height>319</height>
        <left>743</left>
        <top>39</top>
        <visible/>
        <width>755</width>
    </Label>
